Line3.B79AB: I do remember... they were looking for sell-swords. I s'pose on account of the curate - he wasn't a fighting man.
Line5.B79AB: They picked up three. Only Sev's come back.
Line7.B79AB: Out near the cove. She's not right, mind you. Won't talk to people without her mead.
Line9.B79AB: I've got some for her if you've got the coin.
